description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '15 Minute Guided Breathwork To Help Release Stuck Energy & Emotions' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: 15 Minute activating breathwork routine to help clear any emotional blockages and bring you into a state of relaxation and clarity.
